  completionMessage: Policy, caucus and public record reviewed. Azad ki state leadership
    ab process se earned hai.
  chapterNumber: 14
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 14 / PRADESH KA NETRUTVA
  introMessage: Six seats ka foothold mila hai. Ab policy, unity aur public trust
    se leadership earn karo.
  objectives:
  - {fileID: 71402819}
  - {fileID: 1559383617}
  - {fileID: 1264057160}
