  - Mandate, caucus charter and costed budget ready. Ab public hearings and leadership
    bench build karo.
  - Hearings, council, emergency plan and leadership decision complete. Research
    and public record next hain.
  - Research, fact-check and state convention complete. Final ethics audit selection
    decide karega.
